(10, 'brooklyn', '<div class = \"brooklyn\" >\r\n  <div class=\"title2\">\r\n    <h1>Brooklyn</h1>\r\n    <h1>布鲁克林</h1>\r\n    <div class=\"line2\"></div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class = \"wrapper\">\r\n    <header class=\"facts\">\r\n      <h1>~~ Welcome to Brooklyn ~~</h1>\r\n    </header>\r\n    <div class=\"main\">\r\n      <p>The City of New York is the most populous city in the United States and also in the New York State. New York City consists of five boroughs – Brooklyn, Queens, Manhattan, The Bronx, and Staten Island. However, Brooklyn is the most populous borough of New York City. There are estimated 2.649 million residents in 2017. Brooklyn was named after the village of BreukelenIn, it borders the Queens and end of Long Island. In Brooklyn, there are not only have a lot of parks and other attractions, there also have a lot of good restaurant. I have been to many famous places in Brooklyn and the Brooklyn bridge impressed me most.  </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <iframe class = \"map\" src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d387496.7794873144!2d-74.22449630527443!3d40.644907068657325!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x89c24416947c2109%3A0x82765c7404007886!2sBrooklyn%2C+NY!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1551823800556\"></iframe>\r\n\r\n</div>'),
